{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_09_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏祭り当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "会場、まだ夕方なのに凄く賑わってます\nお祭りって、こんなに沢山人が来るんですね",
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日のお祭りは、日本有数の規模だからな\nこの後ステージが控えてるけど、緊張してないか？",
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.233333226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私一人でのステージですからね\nお気遣いありがとうございます",
      "startTime": 23.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大丈夫です。ソロで舞台に立つ機会は\n少ないですけど、ワクワクしてるくらいですから",
      "startTime": 28.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは心強いな。瑠依のパフォーマンスで盛り上げて\n地方の人達にもアピールしていこう",
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頑張ります\n……ところで、まだ本番まで時間がありますよね？",
      "startTime": 41.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなので、少しだけお祭りを\n見て回りたいんですけど……いいでしょうか？",
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時間はあるし、構わないけど\n分かった、それなら俺も一緒に行くよ",
      "startTime": 54.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "人が沢山いる場所に、瑠依を一人で送り出せないからな\n俺が一緒じゃ、あんまり楽しめないかもしれないけど",
      "startTime": 62.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 66.0999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！\nあ……大きな声を出してしまってすみません",
      "startTime": 68.3475369826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.933333226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "別に、嫌とかそういうのはありませんし\n{user}さんがいてくれた方が安心です",
      "startTime": 76.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 83.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、早速ですけど見に行きましょう\nどんな出店があるか、楽しみですね",
      "startTime": 83.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、せっかくだしお祭りも目一杯満喫しよう",
      "startTime": 86.5999998927,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5899.9949138,
          "startTime": 92.4999948065
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 92.2499948065
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 92.2499948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　{user}さん\nあそこにヨーヨーすくいがありますよ！",
      "startTime": 95.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 98.1999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "あっちは射的です、本当に銃で撃つんですね\nやったことありますか？",
      "startTime": 102.3999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 104.3333281398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あの子達が食べてるチョコバナナ\nとっても可愛く飾り付けがされていますね",
      "startTime": 107.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 115.3339807709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "どこの屋台で売っているんでしょう？　美味しそう……\nでも、りんご飴といちご飴も気になるし……",
      "startTime": 115.3339807709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依？　声のトーンを少し抑えてだな……",
      "startTime": 119.56665893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 123.6999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません\nつい、はしゃぎ過ぎてしまって",
      "startTime": 125.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 128.4999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "あの……実は私、お祭りって、小さい頃に\n母に一度、連れて行ってもらって以来なんです",
      "startTime": 133.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 137.3666614731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになってからは、今日みたいに\nお仕事で参加することは何度かありましたけど……",
      "startTime": 139.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "こうして一人のお客さんとして参加するのは\n本当に久しぶりなので、なんだか楽しくって",
      "startTime": 146.4666493733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 151.0999825994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……なら、今日くらいは\n多少はしゃいでも構わないよ。俺も付いてるしな",
      "startTime": 154.53331604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 158.366649266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……ありがとうございます\nそれじゃあ、目一杯楽しませてもらいますね",
      "startTime": 162.2666493733,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3400.0050863000124,
          "startTime": 165.6666544596
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 165.6666544596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "あ……お腹が……\nその、今日はお昼を食べていなかったので",
      "startTime": 169.0666534423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのは分かるが、食事を抜くのは良くないぞ\nそれじゃ、屋台で何か買って食べよう",
      "startTime": 177.533320109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 181.533320109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "伝統的なお祭りでも、いろんなフードがあるんですね\nあそこの大きなお肉の塊は、雑誌で見たことがあります",
      "startTime": 187.2666534423,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "あれはドネルケバブだな\n屋台で見るのは初めてだが、美味しそうだ",
      "startTime": 193.9999867756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 197.2999785303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
